<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.7">
<l>pañcicci ṟukūḻai yuruvāki maruvāta</l>
<l>vañcappeṇ nañcuṇṭa vaṇṇalmuṉ naṇṇāta</l>
<l>kañcaikka ṭantavaṉūr kaṭaṉmallait talacayaṉam</l>
<l>neñcilto ḻuvārait toḻuvāyeṉ tūyneñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My pure heart, worship those who worship in their hearts Talacayaṉam</l>
<l>At Mallai by the sea, the city of him who once overpowered shameless Kaṁsa,</l>
<l>The lord who ate poison from a deceitful, uncaring woman</l>
<l>Having an appearance with sparse, bushy hair.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
